    </p>
    <p>
    <!-- Formattting the url. The link to the server is hardcoded in, then the ids are added with the more variable erb tags.
    And we user a href so you don't have to actually see the ugle URL. --!>
    <a href="http://54.235.20.117:3000/confirm_friendship?uid=<%= @friend.id %>&fid=<%= @user.id %>">Confirm your friendship!</a>
    </p>
  </body>
